<bibRefCitation id="3213F04237B16D8E225E78A9B81D3F66" author="Varma, SK" journalOrPublisher="Theoretical and Applied Genetics" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B254" refString="Varma, SK, 1981. Flora of Bhagalpur. Today's &amp; Tomorrow's Printers and Publishers, New Delhi." title="Flora of Bhagalpur. Today's &amp; Tomorrow's Printers and Publishers, New Delhi." year="1981">Varma 1981</bibRefCitation>
); Chhattisgarh: ban bhata, kutmi (
<emphasis id="1D6C28C5830CB608B41B46F23312DDD6" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Mooney 120</emphasis>
